'''Gerhard Schaar''' ([[5 March]] [[1919]] in [[Berlin]] <U+2013> [[24 January]] [[1983]] in [[Maseru]], [[Lesotho]]) was a [[Germany|German]] [[U-boat]] commander in [[World War II]] and recipient of the [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross]].

